Package: VerR
Type: Package
Title: Compare the performance and results obtained from different versions of a package
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "LÃ©opold", "Guyot",
      email = "leopoldguyot13@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package offers tools to run expression or scripts inside
 custom R environments. These environments are created with the `renv` package.
 Using these environments it is therefore possible to compare the behaviour
 of different versions of a package.
